{"content": "I need to multiply 305 \u00d7 235 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 305\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 0\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 243 + 0 + 5 = 248\u2081\u2080\n- 235\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 162 + 27 + 5 = 194\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 248 \u00d7 194 = 48,112\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 48112 \u00f7 9 = 5345 r 7\n- 5345 \u00f7 9 = 594 r 1\n- 594 \u00f7 9 = 66 r 0\n- 66 \u00f7 9 = 7 r 3\n- 7 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 7\n\nReading from bottom to top: **73017\u2089**\n\n73017", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 323}